org.apache.ignite.tensorflow.core

Class ProcessManagerWrapper<T,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.tensorflow.core.ProcessManagerWrapper<T,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of process specification delegate working with.
    R - Type of accepted process specifications.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProcessManager<R>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NativeProcessManager, TensorFlowServerManager

    public abstract class ProcessManagerWrapper<T,R>
extends Object
implements ProcessManager<R>
    Process manager wrapper that allows to define how one type of process specification should be transformed into another type of process specification delegate working with and delegate all operations to this delegate.
